OL,4,CCelebrated composer Anthony Payne dies
OL,5, Composer Anthony Payne, who famously
OL,6, completed Elgar's unfinished Third
OL,7, Symphony, has died at the age of 84.
OL,9,FOne of Britain's most-respected
OL,10,Fwriters, he was also a renowned critic,
OL,11,Fwhose books on Schoenberg and Frank
OL,12,FBridge became standard texts.
OL,14,FHis death comes just a month after that
OL,15,Fof his wife, the soprano Jane Manning.
OL,17,F"They were inseparable in life, and I
OL,18,Fsuppose it's not a surprise that he
OL,19,Fwould follow her so soon after," said
OL,20,Fcomposer Colin Matthews on BBC Radio 3.
